Soa3--loh8, tak8-e5 hiong5-hiong5 bo5 koh kong2-oe7, ke3-siok8 pok-hun.
“Lin2 ma7 hou7 goa2 chit8-e5 bin7-chu2, goa2 beh chau2--a koh an2-ne.” Goa2 sit8-chai7 tong3 be7-tiau5.
Ba2-suh kau3-ui7--a, goa2 ka7 kha-bang2 koann7--khi2-lai5, bin7 chhau3-chhau3 beh chiunn7-chhia.
『喂, 不要這樣啦!』洪門講:『你永遠都是我們的大--e5-lah.』
Goa2 bo5 kong2-oe7, ma7 m7-kann2 khoann3--in, sim7-chi2 ma7 m7-kann2 nih bak8-chiu, kiann bak8-sai2 lian3--loh8-lai5.
Chit-pai2 li7-khui, m7-chai tang-si5 chiah koh e7-sai2 khoann3-tioh8 in. Kau3 Tai5-pak, koh si7 sin e5 lang5 kap sin e5 khoan5-keng2.
Tai5-pak kam2 u7 si3-kha-a2 kap ka7 goa2 kong3 kah mi-mi-mauh-mauh e5 kui3-tek?
